OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be dry through the
OL,6,Fmorning with bright or sunny spells
OL,7,Fbut cloud increasing towards midday. A
OL,8,Fcloudier afternoon with some showers
OL,9,Fspreading eastwards.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly cloudy during the
OL,12,Fevening and overnight with further
OL,13,Fshowers. A few clear spells for a time
OL,14,Facross south Aberdeenshire.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FA cloudy start with showery
OL,17,Frain then becoming drier and brighter
OL,18,Flater in the morning. A mainly dry
OL,19,Fafternoon with sunny spells. The odd
OL,20,Fshower over Moray and north
OL,21,FAberdeenshire.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
